Script to replace a block of text by another one in files.
Multilines text to search and replace is hosted in input.txt
Multilines text use to replace inline source is hosted in output.txt
Copy this folder in root of source code hiearchy. Files will be scanned reccursively from root dir.
Script is configured to search in .cpp and .h, this can be customized.
Look replace.sh bash script for details.
